{"status": "RESOLVED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "attachments": [{"creator": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "is_obsolete": 1, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8493854}, {"creator": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2014-09-24T20:09:47Z", "type_id": 748, "creation_date": "2014-09-23T18:41:39Z", "id": 985502, "setter": "adw@mozilla.com"}], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8493919}], "classification": "Client Software", "creator": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "cc": ["adw@mozilla.com", "edilee@mozilla.com", "gavin.sharp@gmail.com", "mcastelluccio@mozilla.com", "mmucci@mozilla.com", "nissan4321@gmail.com", "ttaubert@mozilla.com"], "depends_on": [1135285], "creation_time": "2014-09-23T15:44:46Z", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "All", "cf_status_firefox58": "---", "cf_status_firefox59": "---", "keywords": ["regression"], "summary": "checkSizing() and onPageFirstSized() cause uninterruptible reflows", "cf_last_resolved": "2014-09-25T20:37:08Z", "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 402526, "name": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Tim Taubert [:ttaubert]"}, "severity": "normal", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "assigned_to": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "comment_count": 10, "comments": [{"text": "By accessing |document.documentElement.clientWidth| and calling |.getBoundingClientRect()| for all hidden elements (+ 1) about:newtab causes uninterruptible reflows when the page is first shown.\n\n1) Code that collects telemetry data should not have any performance impact.\n2) There might be a different/better way to determine how many children of #newtab-grid are visible?", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9348095, "time": "2014-09-23T15:44:46Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8493854\n0001-Bug-1071635-Get-rid-of-uninterruptible-reflows-cause.patch\n\nLooks like nsIDOMWindowUtils has everything we need.", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9348612, "time": "2014-09-23T17:12:14Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8493854\n0001-Bug-1071635-Get-rid-of-uninterruptible-reflows-cause.patch\n\nSorry, forgot to run tests. Will need to make some adjustments.", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9349110, "time": "2014-09-23T18:29:33Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8493919\n0001-Bug-1071635-Get-rid-of-uninterruptible-reflows-cause.patch, v2\n\nPasses tests now. Turns out I was actually calculating the wrong index by not ignoring empty cells.", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9349188, "time": "2014-09-23T18:41:39Z"}, {"text": "Looks like this snuck in with bug 1042214. The changes to browser_tabopen_reflow.js which obviously caught this have unfortunately not been reviewed :/", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9355065, "time": "2014-09-24T17:40:32Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to Tim Taubert [:ttaubert] from comment #4)\n> Looks like this snuck in with bug 1042214. The changes to\n> browser_tabopen_reflow.js which obviously caught this have unfortunately not\n> been reviewed :/\nSorry about that. I thought it was explicit that we wanted the reflow to calculate positions for the functionality, so the test was updated for that.", "author": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 9355122, "time": "2014-09-24T17:51:57Z"}, {"text": "Yeah, I assumed this was a quick fix to unbreak the test but we don't actually want sync reflows :) I could maybe add something to the test that explicitly states what the test tries to prevent and who to ask for review? The test itself isn't that clear I think.", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9355137, "time": "2014-09-24T17:53:58Z"}, {"text": "https://tbpl.mozilla.org/?tree=Try&rev=76459c153261", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9359403, "time": "2014-09-25T07:46:11Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/integration/fx-team/rev/f191b431571c", "author": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 9359434, "time": "2014-09-25T07:56:25Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/f191b431571c", "author": "ryanvm@gmail.com", "id": 9362937, "time": "2014-09-25T20:37:08Z"}], "id": 1071635, "priority": "--", "mentors_detail": [], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "Trunk", "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox59": "---", "last_change_time": "2016-11-05T00:26:55Z", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Firefox", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "---", "blocks": [1059558, 1042214, 1050643, 1071638], "qa_contact": "", "see_also": [], "cf_fx_iteration": "35.2", "component": "New Tab Page", "votes": 0, "groups": [], "cf_status_firefox60": "---", "target_milestone": "Firefox 35", "is_cc_accessible": true, "url": "", "creator_detail": {"email": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 402526, "name": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Tim Taubert [:ttaubert]"}, "whiteboard": "", "mentors": [], "cc_detail": [{"email": "adw@mozilla.com", "id": 334927, "name": "adw@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Drew Willcoxon :adw"}, {"email": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 125983, "name": "edilee@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Ed Lee :Mardak (PTO-Mar18)"}, {"email": "gavin.sharp@gmail.com", "id": 103593, "name": "gavin.sharp@gmail.com", "real_name": ":Gavin Sharp [email: gavin@gavinsharp.com]"}, {"email": "mcastelluccio@mozilla.com", "id": 420453, "name": "mcastelluccio@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Marco Castelluccio [:marco]"}, {"email": "mmucci@mozilla.com", "id": 458208, "name": "mmucci@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Marco Mucci [:MarcoM]"}, {"email": "nissan4321@gmail.com", "id": 414417, "name": "nissan4321@gmail.com", "real_name": "Mikel"}, {"email": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "id": 402526, "name": "ttaubert@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Tim Taubert [:ttaubert]"}], "cf_has_str": "---", "alias": null, "dupe_of": null, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "firefox-backlog", "modification_date": "2014-09-25T07:59:23Z", "type_id": 846, "creation_date":